    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">Scrabble dictionaries evolve with language. Every update brings hundreds of new words reflecting how we actually speak — from tech jargon that's gone mainstream to food terms borrowed from other cultures. Knowing these additions before your opponents gives you a real competitive edge at the board.</p>

