    <p>Not every trendy word makes it. Abbreviations (LOL, BRB) are excluded because they're acronyms. Proper nouns (Google, TikTok) never qualify. Words with non-standard characters (naïve, café) must be playable without diacritics. The process typically takes 3-5 years from mainstream usage to dictionary inclusion.</p>

